data.description: 100% USDA Conventional Financing Available, NO PMI! Charming ranch style 3 bed/2 bath with a large fenced in front yard, recently updated with newer flooring and paint coming soon! Walk into a wonderful family room boasting a large beautiful stone fireplace, along with a built-in wet bar, great for entertaining family and friends! Light and bright kitchen which features a great amount counter space and cabinets for all your kitchen needs. Each bedroom has drawers/shelves within closets for ideal storage and organization. Step out to a large backyard with a covered concrete patio, with a serene tree and sky view to relax and enjoy our California weather!  This home also features an amp panel that can be used for RVs. A unique property that makes you feel at home, don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
